Package com.rb.nonbiz.collections

Class DoubleMap<K>

java.lang.Object
com.rb.nonbiz.collections.DoubleMap<K>
All Implemented Interfaces:
PrintsMultilineString, java.lang.Iterable<Weighted<K>>
public class DoubleMap<K>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Weighted<K>>, PrintsMultilineString
A thin layer on top of a plain RBMap, for the special case where the values are doubles.

It lets you express more explicitly what a map contains. It also has well-defined functionality for summing, combining etc. - see DoubleMaps.
